ing: 6 boneless chicken breast halves, cooked and diced
1 teaspoon salt-free herb and spice blend
des: "This is so easy, quick and delicious! This can be made ahead of time and used as needed. Presto, chicken salad-o!"
ins: Combine the chicken, celery, spice blend and mayonnaise. Mix all together; more or less mayonnaise can be added, depending on your preference. Voila, your summer salad is ready to serve!
